data.content:
verb
/ˌʌnˈfriːz/ -freezes; -froze /-ˈfroʊz/ ; -freezing
to stop being frozen or to cause (something) to stop being frozen :thaw [no obj]
We can't wait until the ground unfreezes so we can start gardening. [+ obj]
The warm weather unfroze the lake.
[+ obj] :to allow (money or property) to be used, spent, etc.
The Justice Department agreed to unfreeze the company's assets.
to start working properly again [no obj]
I had to wait for my computer to unfreeze before I could read my e-mail. [+ obj]
He helped me to unfreeze my computer.

Động từ
(unfroze; unfrozen)
làm tan băng
unfreeze some chops
làm tan băng ở mấy miếng thịt sườn ra
giải tỏa (tài khoản, tín dụng…)
unfreeze trade restrictions
giải tỏa các hạn chế kinh doanh
